name: Lil Lily
description:
The first flower of my garden. 
You might wonder what's wrong with it by the look on its face.
Well, that's the peculiarity of my garden...
my flowers are watered with coffee.
That's why the psychotic look in it eyes. 
Anyway, your collection would look prettier with a little flower. 

Fun fact: this flower hypnotizes the person who buys it, so if you do it you will have the same look for 24 hours.
